---
import '@fontsource/luckiest-guy';
---
<style>
.landing-page-2 .title{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: "Luckiest Guy", cursive;
    font-size: 50px;
    font-style: normal;
    color:var(--color-azul-oscuro)
}

.landing-page-2 .card-container{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction:row;
    justify-content: space-evenly;

}

.landing-page-2 .card{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    height: 270px;
    width: 270px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 50px ;
    background-color: var(--color-azul-medio);
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    color:var(--color-celeste);
    padding: 5px;
}

.card h2{
    display: flex;
    font-size:20px;
    padding: 20px; 
}

.card p {
    display: flex;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
}

.explanation{
    display:flex;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin: 30px;
}

.call-to-action{
    border-radius: 50px;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: auto;
}

.call-to-action-text{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: var(--color-azul-medio);
    border-radius: 50px;
    width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.call-to-action-text h2{
    font-family: "Luckiest Guy", cursive;
    font-size: 40px;
    color:var(--color-celeste);
</style>

<div class="landing-page-2">
    <div class="title">
        <h2>¿Cómo funciona?</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="using-benefits-section">
        <div class="back-line"></div>
        <div class="card-container"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="explanation">
        <p>¡Cada reencuentro cuenta! Da el primer paso para reunir a más mascotas con sus familias.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="call-to-action">
        <div class="call-to-action-text">
        <h2>¡Únete a la búsqueda!</h2>
    </div>


</div>